      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your musical training and virtuosic reflexes allow you to get more sound out of your sonic and musical weaponry.</p>\n<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Profession (musician) 5 ranks</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you make a full attack with a weapon that does sonic damage or has the professional (musician) weapon special property, your attacks deal an additional 1d6 sonic damage on a successful hit. Additionally, when you score a critical hit with a weapon that deals sonic damage or has the professional (musician) weapon special property, in addition to any other critical hit effect you would apply, you also apply the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.O5GDQUKPCJ9Zbnfj.JournalEntryPage.zOJ86MDq6kNzAAbB#deafen]{deafen} critical hit effect. If the weapon already has the deafen critical hit effect, increase its DC by 2.</p>"
